btw file uploads in Build / Converse projects or app / deployment runs will not work on aihub-sandbox, crafting-aihub, crafting-cyp (basically all environments deployed off master) because of this issue (https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C04TSMWLPAS/p1732580007520369)

i just tested on each environment, and indexing always fails :disappointed:
this means that Cypress CI will likely fail on all PRs (example (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/65470)) :sob:
